data.description: Cape Cod ready for a new owner! The front porch spans across the entire front of the house and around one side. The back deck was made for entertaining! Inside you’ll find the owner’s bedroom and bathroom, as well as the main living areas- living, kitchen, dining, and laundry rooms are all on the main level. Upstairs are 2 secondary rooms with a shared bathroom. On the garage/basement level is a bedroom with a bonus room that is currently being used as a bedroom. Back outside you’ll see the two car garage and around the back to see additional storage under the massive deck. The home is located in Calloway Estates in Rockmart which is a quick drive to downtown Rockmart, Cedartown, and easy access to 278 for all commuters to Atlanta. Grab a showing today to see it yourself!
